; A simple sample to check loop behavior.
;
; - Loops can be nested.
; - By using ':', only the innermost loop can be exited early.

#tempo 120
#denom 4
#key =

@bell
1 1 0 1 0 0
	1 8.5 0 0 1 0 1

; | d d8c8 a g | g a g a | d a g a | d a d8c8 a |
; | d d8c8 a g | g a g a | d a g a | d f g    a |
melody @bell [d>d8c8<ag [ga]2 : [da:ga]2 >d8c8<a]2 daga dfga
